org.openstack4j.model.compute

Interface Server

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelEntity, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NovaServer

    public interface Server
extends ModelEntity
    A server is a virtual machine instance on a compute based system.
    Author:
    Jeremy Unruh
